            I record in a fully soundproofed booth equipped with a Scarlet Focusrite audio interface, an NT1A microphone, and use Ableton Live 12 for editing.
            My internet speeds are 747 Mbps download and 344 Mbps upload, ensuring high-quality, reliable communication and performance.
        </p>
